thread.title: Christy Cheng

author: Christy Cheng
title: Christy Cheng
text: Recently bought an iPhone 7 wallet case from Casetify in honey bee pattern. It was so pretty and convenient. Having used for almost 2 weeks, I found it very handy because it includes a SIM pin and a space to place your sim card - perfect for travel (my pin and sim cards were always gone:(( ), not to mention the wallet part of the case. They also do sweet packaging with a thank you card attached. Would surely recommend it to my friends ;)
